# ❌ Common Mistakes

## ❌ Forgetting START or STOP

Wrong

```text
OUTPUT "Hello"
```

Correct

```text
START

OUTPUT "Hello"

STOP
```

---

## ❌ Using Variables Without INPUT

Wrong

```text
SET SUM = A + B

OUTPUT SUM
```

Correct

```text
START

INPUT A

INPUT B

SET SUM = A + B

OUTPUT SUM

STOP
```

---

## ❌ Forgetting OUTPUT

Wrong

```text
START

INPUT A

INPUT B

SET SUM = A + B

STOP
```

Correct

```text
START

INPUT A

INPUT B

SET SUM = A + B

OUTPUT SUM

STOP
```

